1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:21,880
Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by all here.

2
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:41,080
We will now begin five rounds consisting of three minutes each, one minute pause in between.

3
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:59,920
We shall begin the first round in ten seconds.

4
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:25,320
Round one. Visualize the cosmic sky.

5
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:31,320
Look at the night sky.

6
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:39,320
See the stars.

7
00:01:39,320 --> 00:02:02,320
See the cosmic sky.

8
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:27,320
Allow the stars to move closer to you and look at the dark space between the stars.

9
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:48,320
Allow the stars to shift away as you move towards darkness.

10
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:58,320
Look at the darkness.

11
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:18,320
See the dark space.

12
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:36,320
Look at the darkness, approaching your face.

13
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:54,320
Look at the dark.

14
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:16,320
Look at the dark.

15
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:26,320
Look at the dark.

16
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:54,320
Round two.

17
00:04:56,320 --> 00:05:12,320
Visualize the full moon inside your chest.

18
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:30,320
Look at the full moon inside you.

19
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:56,320
The moon and the moonlight lighting up your chest.

20
00:05:57,320 --> 00:06:14,320
Here's the dark.

21
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:26,320
Coming upward through your throat.

22
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:46,320
Look at the shining moon inside you.

23
00:06:46,320 --> 00:07:04,320
See the full moon.

24
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:33,320
Full moon inside your chest.

25
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:44,320
Through your chest, lighting on your throat.

26
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:49,320
Your head.

27
00:07:49,320 --> 00:08:00,320
See the full moon.

28
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:29,320
End of round two.

29
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:57,320
Round three.

30
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:24,320
Now visualize the star in your belly right in the center of gravity.

31
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:38,320
Look at the shining star.

32
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:54,320
Surrounded by darkness of the belly.

33
00:09:55,320 --> 00:10:12,320
Sense the star in the starlight emanating from your center.

34
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:26,320
Lighting up through your body.

35
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:46,320
Shining vertically to the center of your head.

36
00:10:46,320 --> 00:11:07,320
Look at the shining star.

37
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:17,320
Keep looking.

38
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:27,320
The starlight.

39
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:59,320
The starlight.

40
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:09,320
End of round three.

41
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:39,320
Round four.

42
00:12:39,320 --> 00:13:03,320
Round four.

43
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:21,320
Let us look at the star deep in the center of gravity.

44
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:35,320
Surrounded by darkness of the belly.

45
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:47,320
The increasing and expanding darkness.

46
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:59,320
Starts to cover the starlight.

47
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:19,320
As the star fades away into the darkness.

48
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:37,320
Look at the darkness surrounding the center of gravity.

49
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:51,320
Gaze at the darkness of the belly.

50
00:14:51,320 --> 00:15:01,320
Look at the space of dark.

51
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:06,320
Deep in the belly.

52
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:21,320
The vast darkness below.

53
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:42,320
Look at the vast darkness.

54
00:15:42,320 --> 00:16:00,320
Continue to look at the dark in the belly.

55
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:10,320
End of round four.

56
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:56,320
Round five.

57
00:16:56,320 --> 00:17:14,320
Now visualize the cosmic sky in front of you.

58
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:32,320
Gaze at stars then at the darkness.

59
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:42,320
Move closer to the stars.

60
00:17:42,320 --> 00:18:02,320
Disappear away.

61
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:20,320
Move beyond stars towards darkness.

62
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:44,320
See the deep dark beyond all planets, galaxies, darkness in front of you.

63
00:18:50,320 --> 00:19:16,320
Darkness approaching to your face.

64
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:36,320
Touch the darkness.

65
00:19:36,320 --> 00:20:00,320
Stay in the dark.

66
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:20,320
End of round five.

67
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:54,320
Round six.

68
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:20,320
Visualize a single star in the dark sky.

69
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:38,320
Start starlight coming in your direction.

70
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:52,320
See how the star is moving closer to you.

71
00:21:52,320 --> 00:22:12,320
The sun is forming into an image of sun in front of you.

72
00:22:12,320 --> 00:22:34,320
The sun is moving closer.

73
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:48,320
The giant sun in front of you.

74
00:22:48,320 --> 00:23:10,320
The space of sun.

75
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:30,320
The sunlight.

76
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:54,320
You merge into the sun.

77
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:20,320
End of round six.

